  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666510/extras/39e58794f216b151e3b948b2762006b7.avif?t=1749284234\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666510/extras/75df176c15609d3e856d3f69f2105dcb.poster.avif?t=1749284234\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666510/extras/75df176c15609d3e856d3f69f2105dcb.webm?t=1749284234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666510/extras/671c6cf06428fd306b83f93e8180eeca.avif?t=1749284234\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The evil organization Fakker has been terrorizing the residents of the city at night, abducting people left and right. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One woman stands against them: Magical Valkyrie Frostia, a transforming hero who takes down any villains who stand against her. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, she saves another woman with the potential to transform and fight alongside her. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will her new friend be able to transform into Magical Valkyrie Lyristia and stop Fakker's misdeeds for good?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic RPG Experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leveling System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contemporary Setting</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666510/extras/39e58794f216b151e3b948b2762006b7.avif?t=1749284234\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666510/extras/75df176c15609d3e856d3f69f2105dcb.poster.avif?t=1749284234\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666510/extras/75df176c15609d3e856d3f69f2105dcb.webm?t=1749284234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666510/extras/671c6cf06428fd306b83f93e8180eeca.avif?t=1749284234\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The evil organization Fakker has been terrorizing the residents of the city at night, abducting people left and right. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One woman stands against them: Magical Valkyrie Frostia, a transforming hero who takes down any villains who stand against her. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, she saves another woman with the potential to transform and fight alongside her. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will her new friend be able to transform into Magical Valkyrie Lyristia and stop Fakker's misdeeds for good?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic RPG Experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leveling System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contemporary Setting</p></li></ul>",
